title: Will a "million Marsh Militia " try to stop the launch of Biden?
subtitle: Given the troubled 2020 election season, some disturbances are expected.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: In January 2021, millions of people will gather in the "Melitia March" in Washington, D.C., in the hope of preventing the inauguration of President-elect Joe Biden, and protecting the capital and national monuments from "left-wing rebels who have proven violence."
